Interface Expendable

All Known Subinterfaces:

All Known Implementing Classes:
AEImage, AEShaderResource, AssetContainer, AssetManager, EngineLoader, ForwardAmbientShader, ForwardDirectionalShader, ForwardPointShader, ForwardSpotShader, GenericCache, GLFWWindow, GLFWWindow.AnimatedCursor, GLFWWindow.StaticCursor, GLFWWindow.StaticCursorResource, GLFWWindowManager, MainGame, Mesh, Mesh.MeshResource, ModelScene, PixelMap, RenderingEngine, Shader, Texture, TwoFactorGenericCache, WireFrameShader
public interface Expendable
An interface used to identify and organize entitys which can be destroyed at run time or at the end of runtime. Caution: Implementing this interface means that the object CAN be destroyed, unlike static objects which last for all runtime.
